(14, 1, 0, 'GRDJEV01I010014', 0, NULL, 'Design and Development of Deployable Mechanism for Space Borne Large Size Antenna Structure', 'Aerospace, Machine Design', 2, 6, '', 'Deployable reflector, solid surface antenna, deployment mechanism.', 'The reflector antenna is used in space craft for reflecting back the electromagnetic waves. The main aim of present work is to increase the diameter of solid reflector in space after deployed. This paper presents the different configuration for solid surface deployable antenna. The antenna surface is divided into three parts and fold by motor attached at connecting rod. This new folding technique has significant advantages over number of existing concept both in terms of packaged size and mechanical simplicity.', '', 'Akash M Patel', 'Department of Mechanical Engineering B.V.M. Engineering College', 'amp_jb@yahoo.com', '9714471646', '21-Green park society part-5', 'modhera road mehsana-2 ', 'Mehsana', '384002', 'Gujrat', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I01/0014/1451021975_Design-and-Development-of-Deployable-Mechanism-for-Space-Borne-Large-Size-Antenna-Structure.docx', '', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', NULL, 1, 'GRDJE/V01/I01/0014/', '3', 0, 0, 0, '2015-12-25 11:09:35', 0, '2015-12-28 10:52:47', 1, 1),
