(64, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040081', 39, NULL, 'Modification and Installation of Plate Rolling Machine', 'mechanical Engg', 2, 6, '', 'Rolling Machine, Gear Drive, Belt and Pulley, Motor', 'The paper deals with replacing the belt and pulley drive with gear box for bending of sheet by using plate rolling machine .Especially\r\nDiscussion made the productivity analysis of belt and pulley drive machine to gear box operated plate rolling machine. Considering belt and pulley drive operation is replaced by gear power operated devices. It also gives information about limitation of belt and pulley operated sheet bending machine. Such as slipping of belt, coming out of plate without bending operation.\r\n', '', 'Jadhav Mahesh J', 'S.B Patil. College Of Engg, Indapur', 'maheshjadhav218@gmail.com', '9860242303', 'A/p:Galandwadi no 2 tal:Indapur Dist:Pune', 'INdapur', 'Indapur', '413106', 'Maharashtra', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0081/1458544398_publish-paper31.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Disagree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Disagree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Disagree","Material method was given with company detail":"Disagree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Disagree","Method was describe in details":"Disagree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Disagree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Disagree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Disagree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Disagree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in this journal":"Disagree","comment":"Paper: Modification And Installation Of Plate Rolling Machine\\r\\n\\r\\nNo technical data has been provided. What was the result prior to modification and post modification has not been discussed. No research papers have been referred, only websites an