(65, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040082', 52, NULL, 'Survey on Security for Online Voting System', 'Network secuity', 5, 4, '', 'Cryptography', 'The word “vote” means to choose from a list, to elect or to determine. The main goal of voting is to come up with leaders of people’s choice. Many fields came up with Online voting systems. These online voting systems have issues regarding security of vote. As we know there are many online voting systems developed earlier but they have several security issues regarding authentication, integrity and non-repudiation. Thus to avoid such issues there should be some secure approach for tackling them. We are trying to provide some with our project.', '', 'Kalyani Sanjay Khandar', 'Rajiv Gandhi College of Engineering and Research', 'kalyanikhandar@gmail.com', '9689283081', 'P61, lavkush nagar, ', 'Manewada, Ring Road ', 'Nagpur', '440027', 'Maharashtra', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0082/1458555550_Grd-paper.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Disagree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Disagree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Disagree","Material method was given with company detail":"Disagree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Disagree","Method was describe in details":"Disagree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Disagree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Disagree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Disagree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Disagree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in this journal":"Disagree","comment":"Reviewer comments of the paper : Survey on Security for Online Voting System\\r\\n   1.\\tPaper is not in the Journal  format\\r\\n    2.   The affiliation details of the authors  are  not in the correct format (Qualification \\r\\n           and the designation lik