(80, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040087', 80, NULL, 'MOBILE DEVICE BASED VOTING SYSTEM USING THE VISUAL CRYPTOGRAPHY', 'network security', 1, 11, '', 'Mobile Voting, Private Key, Mobile SMS, Visual Cryptography, Secured Network.', 'Mobile Voting System (MVS) is a very secure, efficient and easy way to casting of vote. Mobile Voting System creating Online Voting System. All user will enter their details in verification form, server will check whether they are valid user or not. If it is valid, user server provide user Id and Password. By using Application Program Interface (API) and generating One Time Password number administrator will send to the user by using One Time Password number Encryption and Decryption and also visual cryptography. Security providing double time encryption and decryption using visual cryptography. If the hacker tried to hack it will be displayed image or video. System provide a new Electronic Voting (E-Voting) system which full fills the security requirements of voting process. In this paper total three steps are required: Online Registration of the vote casting system for voters and displaying the result. There is a need for the usage of internet for voting purpose. It is required at the time of online registration only. All process will be done through Short Message Service messaging with requirement of internet connection.', '', 'Anamica S', 'Anna University Regional Campus, Coimbatore', 'anamicas90@gmail.com', '9566606625', 'Seyyalure Vill', 'Ettivayal Post', 'Ramanathapuram Dist', '623527', 'Tamilnadu', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0087/1458640409_journal-gudppr1.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Partial Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Partial Agree","Method was describe in details":"Agree","Method was d