(85, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040092', 127, NULL, 'PROVIDING PRIVACY AND REDUCING TIME CONSUMPTION IN CROSS CLOUD SERVICE COMPOSITION', 'CLOUD COMPUTING', 1, 11, '', 'Cloud, Cross Cloud,  Hiresome-II, Indexed Based Searching, Service Composition.', 'Cross cloud computing is the piece of software that is portable and can run on multiple platforms without human intervention. Cross cloud service composition provides a concrete approach that is capable for large scale big data processing. We propose a privacy-aware cross-cloud service composition method, named Hire Some-II (History record-based Service optimization method) based on its previous basic version Hire Some-I. In our method, to enhance the credibility of a composition plan, the evaluation of a service is promoted by some of its Qos history records. Using Hiresome-II technique time consumption for searching of data can be reduced. Cloud computing is an internet based computing, which shares resources, software and information are provided to computers and other devices on demand, in this security is the major concern.', '', '  D. Jayakumari', 'RVS College of Engineering and Technology', 'dgjeyakumari@gmail.com', '9842603569', 'RVS College of Engineering and Technology', 'KUMARANKOTTAM CAMPUS, KANNAMPALAYAM', 'COIMBATORE', '641402', 'TAMILNADU', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0092/1458715886_grd-journal.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Agree","Method was describe in details":"Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Agree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Agree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was r