(87, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040094', 48, NULL, 'Parametric Studies in Design of Staging Configuration for Elevated Service Reservoir for Seismic Consideration: A Review  ', 'Structural Engineering ', 2, 18, '', 'Circular water tank, Bracings, Staad pro, Seismic, tagging system.', 'Earthquake being one of the most dangerous and hazardous kind of natural disaster which not only leads to loss of human life but also causes economic loss.  Hence utmost care is necessary for designing any structure specially elevated structure which are more likely to get affected by earthquake. Stability of water tank due to earthquake depends upon the supporting structure provided to elevated water tank. More the stability of the supporting structure more it is safe in earthquake point of view. Stability of supporting structure can be achieved by providing bracing patterns. So selection of bracings patterns plays an important role in achieving stability of water tank in earthquake prone areas.', '', 'PAWAN SUHAS NEMADE', 'YESHWANTRAO CHAVAN COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING', 'psnemade1@gmail.com', '9921130002', '38 RAVINDRA NAGAR ', 'NEAR PRATAP NAGAR', 'NAGPUR', '440022', 'MAHARASHTRA', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0094/1458722344_Review-Paper-2.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Fully Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Fully Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Fully Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Fully Agree","Method was describe in details":"Fully Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Fully Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Fully Agree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Fully Agree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Agree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in t