(88, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040095', 89, NULL, 'AN IMPROVED PARALLEL PROCESSING BY QUERY OPTIMIZATION IN CLOUD ENVIRONMENT  AN IMPROVED PARALLEL PROCESSING BY QUERY OPTIMIZATION IN CLOUD ENVIRONMENT AN IMPROVED PARALLEL PROCESSING BY QUERY OPTIMIZATION IN CLOUD ENVIRONMENT ', 'Cloud Computing', 1, 12, '', 'Cloud Computing', 'Transfer speed effective execution of online enormous information examination in telecom systems requests for customized arrangements. Existing gushing investigation frameworks are intended to work in extensive server farms, accepting boundless transmission capacity between server farm hubs. Applying these arrangements unmodified to disperse telecom mists, neglects the way that accessible transfer speed is a rare and expensive asset making the telecom system significant to end-clients. This article presents Continuous Hive ,a gushing investigation stage custom-made for appropriated telecom mists. The principal commitment of CHive is that it streamlines inquiry arrangements to minimize their general data transfer capacity utilization when sent in a circulated telecom cloud. Moreover, these enhanced inquiry arranges have a high level of parallelism implicit, profiting rate of execution. Early examinations on information from an extensive portable administrator demonstrate that CHive can yield data transmission.\r\n', '', 'Sivaram.S.E', 'Velammal Institute of technology', 'siva028111@gmail.com', '8189952816', 'no:9,1st floor', 'new shasthri nagar', 'kolathur', '600099', 'tamil nadu', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0095/1458740055_journelnew1.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Partial Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Partial Agree","Method was describe in details":"Partial Agree","Method was describe with quantity of