(104, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040098', 125, NULL, 'EFFICIENT SEARCH OF DATA IN CLOUD COMPUTING USING CUMULATIVE KEY', 'CLOUD COMPUTING', 1, 4, '', 'aggregate key, ciphertext, cloud storage, public key cryptosystem, secret key', 'Cloud computing relies on sharing of resources to obtain coherence and economies of scale similar to a utility over a network.In the proposed system,we introduce the multi keyword search mechanism so the users can search in the cloud easily according to their search.In proposed system new public-key cryptosystems is proposed to securely, efficiently, and easily share data with others in cloud storage.The main idea is that one can aggregate any set of secret keys and make them as compact as a single key, but all keys should be aggregated.In other words, the secret key holder can release a fixed-size aggregate key for convenient choices of ciphertext set in cloud storage, but the other encrypted files outside the set remain confidential. We can share the data efficiently and securely.This method is more flexible than hierarchical key assignment. This method is very convenient and share data in selective way.', '', 'Kiruthika.R', 'KPR INSTITUTE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY,Coimbatore', 'kirthika2794@gmail.com', '9042331831', '77/36,palaniappa nagar 1st street', 'Sowripalayam', 'Coimbatore', '641028', 'Tamilnadu', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0098/1458793673_journal-paper.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Partial Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Partial Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Partial Agree","Method was describe in details":"Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Disagree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Applic