(106, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040100', 103, NULL, 'Real- time traffic light control using image processing', 'Image processing', 6, 7, '', 'Image processing, traffic light control, real time image capture, vehicle counting, blob detection technique', 'As the number of vehicles on the road increases,to control and manage  this heavy traffic it becomes extremely difficult.So the proposed system uses a webcam mounted  to observe the traffic on the road.On each captured image,we are using different image processing techniques and based on the result the priority is set.On the basis of the priority, the duration of traffic light on each lane is allocated.Then a lane which is having heavy traffic , green light signal is turned on for a long time.Also we are using MATLAB programming in simulating and developing the system.', '', 'MIR ANAM NISAR AHMED', 'M.H. SABOO SIDDIK COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING', 'miranam1994@gmail.com', '9867776062', '202,SAGARIKA BLDG,MBPT OFFICER QTRS,OPPOSITE MAZGAON DOCK,', 'DOCKYARD ROAD,MUMBAI-400010', 'MUMBAI', '400010', 'MAHARASHTRA', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0100/1458801706_traffic-IP.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Disagree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Disagree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Partial Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Disagree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Disagree","Method was describe in details":"Disagree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Disagree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Disagree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Disagree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Disagree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in this journal":"Disagree","comment":"The flowchart of work is not explained good. There is no novelty in paper because concept 