(107, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040101', 121, NULL, 'AN INTELLIGENT TRACKING SYSTEM BASED ON GSM AND GPS USING ANDROID APPLICATION', 'EMBEDDED SYSTEM', 1, 7, '', ': GSM module, GPS receiver, Arduino board, Android mobile with track application, LCD, ignition control.', 'Personal Tracking Systems are the tracking devices specially built up for personal information. The person takes it with him and the information of where he is presently is provided. The same system has been implemented in this mobile tracking application i.e. Sensel Tracker. In various extended features that the existing system does not have. This system is GPS enabled android mobile phone whose location is tracked. Our application provides the functionality of defining the geo-fence areas as safe, risky and highly risky. An efficient automotive security system is implemented for anti-theft using an embedded system occupied with a Global Positioning System (GPS) and a Global System of Mobile (GSM). The client interacts through this system with vehicles and determines their current locations and status using track app android application. The user can track the position of targeted vehicles through this app. ', '', 'ADITHYA.M', 'NANDHA ENGINEERING COLLEGE', 'adithyamahes@gmail.com', '9698282074', 'NO-49, NEW AGRAHARAM STREET', 'ERODE-1', 'ERODE', '638001', 'TAMILNADU', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0101/1458802466_journal-GRD.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Fully Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Fully Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Partial Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Partial Agree","Method was describe in details":"Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Partial Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Agree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Ap