(112, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040106', 129, NULL, 'A REVIEW PAPER ON MEMORY TESTING USING BIST', 'VLSI', 2, 7, '', 'Built-in Self-Test, Random Access Memory, CUT circuit under test, TPG Test Pattern Generation, Response Analysis', 'In this review paper, Built-in self-test has been studied. This Built-in Self-Test (BIST) technique not only helpful from economically but also it gives test logic for  the test pattern. This paper concluded basic test problems and some reliable methods of solution discussed in this paper while studied level of BIST. The basic concept of BIST that  it provide a path by which system could test itself.', '', 'Ritu Singh Thakur ', 'Dr. C. V. Raman University kola, Bilaspur (C.G.)', 'ritusingh47873@gmail.com', '9039768772', 'Parijat Extension SMIG c 65 ', 'Gaurav path, near Pallav Bhavan Bilaspur (C.G.), India 495001', 'Bilaspur', '495001', 'chhatisgarh', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0106/1458821439_paper-for-review.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Partial Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Partial Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Agree","Method was describe in details":"Partial Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Partial Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Agree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Partial Agree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Partial Agree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in this journal":"Agree","comment":"this is a review paper if author do some change in paper then publish the paper.\\r\\n 1.keywords-Little more define keywords used in paper. \\r\\n2.Scholarly Quality Concept is good but scholarly quality is matched to some previous authors work.\\r\\