(137, 4, 0, 'GRDJEV01I040124', 87, NULL, 'Power Generation Through Wind Created By Moving Train', 'Electrical Engineering', 5, 8, '', 'Renewable energy, wind turbines, wind. ', 'Many areas aren’t windy and having intermittency behavior of wind is one of the big obstacle to the world wide application of wind power generation .This paper attempts to explain the method of generating  energy through moving train by using windmill .The method for generating electricity is by tapping wind pressure generated by moving train through windmill .The turbine converts wind energy into mechanical energy and this mechanical energy is converted into electrical energy by using generating device. It will be helpful to fulfill the increasing demand of electricity.', '', 'Tupe Sujata Machindra', 'AVCOE, Sangamner', 'sujataele92@gmail.com', '8983315088', 'Kanchan Nagar, ', 'Ambad Road, Jalna', 'Jalna', '431203', 'Maharashtra', 'India', 'GRDJE/V01/I04/0124/1458904440_POWER-GENERATION-THROUGH-WIND-CREATED-BY-MOVING-TRAIN.docx', '{"Title construction of manuscript was good":"Fully Agree","Introduction covers each part of work done area Introduction covers all required thorough":"Fully Agree","Knowledge to understand the topic":"Agree","Material method was given with company detail":"Partial Agree","All materials were covered which was used in that work":"Agree","Method was describe in details":"Agree","Method was describe with quantity of materials used in that work":"Agree","Result was discussed thoroughly to understand the effect of work":"Agree","Result was discussed with mathematical model Application":"Partial Agree","Acknowledgement was described all help which was received during the work":"Agree","I do not have any objection if this work was published in this journal":"Agree","comment":"Recommended. But some Modifications.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Main concept is 40 % unique. So include more explanation and also reference papers should be added."}', 0, '', '', 0, 0, '', NULL, 5, 'GRDJE/V01/I