g></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Assistant Professor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">GANPAT UNIVERSITY-INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Dr. CHETAN DUDHAGARA</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Associate Professor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">N. V. PATEL COLLEGE OF PURE AND APPLIED SCIENCES</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Dr. L.M.Karthikeyan</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Assistant Professor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Noorul Islam University,India</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Prof. Bramha S Tripathi</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Assistant Professor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Bhopal Institute of Technology Bhopal MP</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>KANNADHASAN S</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Research Scholar</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">ANNA UNIVERSITY</p>\r\n</div>', 'editorial-board', 'editorial-board', 'editorial-board', 1, 0, 1, 1438937787, 1, 1458585530),
('faq', 'Frequenty Asked Questions', '', '<div id="accordion" class="panel-group">\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse1" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How can I submit my manuscript to GRD Journals?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">\r\n<div class="panel-body">You can submit your paper to the GRD Journals from the link <a href="../../grdje/submit-an-article">Submit Article</a> or can e-mail us <a href="mailto:mailTo: info@grdjournals.com">info@grdjournals.com</a> if you aren''t able to submit online.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse2" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Can I submit more than one paper for the same issue?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Yes, you can submit more than one paper at a time. But you should keep the id of each and every paper saperate. Any of your papers won''t be co-related.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse3" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How much time does the review process takes?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">We are having dedicated editors in our editorial board The editorial board is highly committed to the quick review process of the paper, but not with the sacrifice of the right judgment of a paper. The review process takes maximum Five days depending upon paperwork.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse4" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">What is the frequency of publication of GRD Journals For Engineering (GRDJE)?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body"><a title="GRD Journals For Engineering(GRDJE)" href="../../grdje" target="_blank">GRD Journals For Engineering(GRDJE)</a>&nbsp;is monthly journal. It publishes one issue per month. However, in some cases, special issues may introduced.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse7" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Is there any restriction for number of pages and fee for extra pages?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Minimum 2 pages and Maximum 7 pages are allowed. If it exceeds 7, remaining will be charged Rs. 100 per page. Make Sure that images in pages are properly aligned and don''t leave too much blank space if not necessary.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse12" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How can I check status of my paper?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Once submitted, You may check your paper status by clicking on following link.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body"><a href="../../check-your-paper-status" target="_blank">Check Paper Status</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse5" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">When I will get to know if my paper is accepted/Rejected?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">You will receive notification for the same by GRD Journals through Email with attached review report which will show review of your paper by reviewer.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse6" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How can I pay the publication fee?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You can pay publication fess by these ways.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">- Online payment through our website.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">- By Using Net Banking.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">- Payment through Bank account transfer to Any BANK (NEFT)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">- Payment by direct (Cash) deposit of fess in Account Payment through Demand Draft.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">In all above mathods , image of payment proof is necessary to be uploaded for verification purpose.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">You will find the account details on site as well as in acceptance mail.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse8" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Why should i transfer copyrights to GRD Journals?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Like many other publishers, GRD Journals requires authors to provide transfer of copyright prior to publication. This permits GRD Journals to publish the article and to defend against improper use i. e. publishing in other journals. It also permits GRD Journals to mount the article online and to use the article in other forms or media. By the GRD Journals transfer agreement, authors retain substantial rights in the work. Copyrights Transfer form is available&nbsp;from following link.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body"><a title="Download Copyright Transfer Form" href="http://grdjournals.com/uploads/files/GRD-copyright.pdf" target="_blank">Download Copyright Transfer Form</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse9" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How long my published paper will be Online?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">It will be online with no expiration. You can find your published papers in Archives&gt;current issue if it belongs from current issue or Archives&gt;past issue if published in earlier issues.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse10" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Is there a template available for paper format?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Yes, you can download paper format from following link.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body"><a href="http://grdjournals.com/uploads/files/GRD-paper-format.pdf" target="_blank">Download Paper Template File(PDF)</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapse11" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How can I join GRD Journals as a reviewer?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">The GRD Journals is an open membership organization. It is a small working group of general Engineering Streams Journals. Occasionally, the GRD Journals will invite a new member or guest when the committee feels that the new journal or organization will provide a needed perspective that is not already available within the existing committee. Open membership organizations for editors and others in Engineering. To join as reviewer please visit GRDJournals.com</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'faq', 'faq', 'faq', 1, 0, 1, 1438939620, 1, 1454620076),
('grdjeabout', 'GRD Journal for Engineering | GRDJE | ISSN 2455-5703', '', '<div class="inneraboutcontent">\r\n<table style="height: 60%;" border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<img style="float: left;" src="https://d3k81ch9hvuctc.cloudfront.net/company/muWbV5/images/bde5e941-188e-45bd-bd90-5f661c7df239.png" alt="GRD Journal for Engineering" width="100" height="80" /></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;">\r\n<table style="height: 60%;" border="0" width="100%&quot;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Executive Editor</strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">:</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">Prof. Mukesh Parmar</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>e-ISSN</strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">:</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">2455-5703</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Publication Frequency</strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">:</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">12 Issue per Year</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Publisher</strong></td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">:</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;">Global Research and Development Journals (GRD Journals)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n<div class="online_wrap">\r\n<div class="journal_block">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>GRD Journal for Engineering&nbsp; (GRDJE)</strong>&nbsp; is an uprising peer-reviewed journal in the field of engineering journal. With simple procedure GRDJE provides a best framework to publish the quality research articles and gives it a global recognition. With a simple manuscript submission procedure GRDJE removes the overburden of complex things from authors through automatic procedure. In addition the review is done by professionals with strong educational background who thoroughly reviews your paper and gives the perfact analysis and suggestions if needed to improvise your research.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>The GRD Journals automated process makes faster publication with indexing into global libraries.</p>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="kmTextContent" style="border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0; mso-table-rspace: 0; color: #222; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 100%; text-align: left; width: 40%; border-top-width: 1px; padding: 4px 0px 4px 0px;" valign="top"><strong><span style="color: #4da8fe;">BENEFITS of GRDJE</span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>Fast review process, peer-reviewed, security, flexible payment mathods,&nbsp; strong support, automated paper status, email and sms notification, open journal, strong review panel.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>So what are you waiting for, we highly appreciate the creative research and believe giving the new researchers chance.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'grdje', 'GRD Journal for Engineering, grdje', 'GRD Journal for Engineering', 1, 0, 1, 1442672212, 1, 1457883240),
